text: @narendramodi Modi ji, @myogiadityanath @UPGovt we are following lockdown very seriously. Request you to  please ensure the availability of essential goods at local market. Vegetables and fruits prices skyrocketed in Kanpur. Please take action. #ISupportJantaCurfew #coronavirus
